.da AFTALE        25mm    45.5mm width 170mm
.da SLID          25mm      56mm width 165mm
.da UNDLEJER      20mm     227mm width 165mm
.**************************************************************************
.ar AFTALE on
.tp 130mm
&AFTALENR.¤&DATO.
.ar off
